==English==
==={{initialism}}===
; '''GAOTU''' : Grand Architect Of The Universe <br> A Supreme Being responsible for the creation of the Universe
**(Freemasonry) General term for Deity, whatever a person's belief system is.
**In Freemasonry, especially for while Brethren are gathered, used as an agreed-upon term for Deity, be it Buddha, Allah, Yahwe, LORD, The Fifth Element, etc.